OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1780575067
OL,3,CEmergency teams highlight open water
OL,4,Cdangers
OL,6,FRescue teams and emergency services
OL,7,Fhave carried out demonstrations at
OL,8,FColdingham Bay to teach people about
OL,9,Fwater safety.
OL,11,FWatch ITV Border reporter Isla Todd's
OL,12,Ffull report:
OL,14,FRecent hot weather has seen a rise in
OL,15,Fthe number of deaths in open water
OL,16,Facross the UK. The beautiful Scottish
OL,17,FBorders coastline, as well as the
OL,18,FGalloway lochs or lakes and tarns of
OL,19,Fthe Lake District have seen tragedies
OL,20,Fin recent years as people head to the
OL,21,Fwater to cool off.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
