OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1780575067
OL,3,CEmergency teams highlight open water
OL,4,Cdangers
OL,6,FA 13-year-old girl is the latest to
OL,7,Fhave lost her life after being pulled
OL,8,Ffrom a river in North Yorkshire.
OL,9,FEmergency services are still searching
OL,10,Ffor a missing 11-year-old boy in the
OL,11,FRiver Don in South Yorkshire.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1780575067
OL,3,CEmergency teams highlight open water
OL,4,Cdangers
OL,6,FBarry Shaw of St Abbs Independent
OL,7,FLifeboat told ITV Border, "With
OL,8,Feverything that's gone on over the
OL,9,Fover the bank holiday, the tragic
OL,10,Fdeaths that we've had, the safety
OL,11,Fmessage needs to get out to families
OL,12,Fand young children and teenagers as
OL,13,Fwell. The cold water can be a killer,
OL,14,Falthough it can be a lot of fun as
OL,15,Fwell."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1780575067
OL,3,CEmergency teams highlight open water
OL,4,Cdangers
OL,6,FColdingham Bay is one of the few
OL,7,Fpopular coastal swimming areas that
OL,8,Fhas lifeguards on duty but the team
OL,9,Fthere have a key message about
OL,10,Fpersonal accountability. They say
OL,11,Femergency teams are on hand for
OL,12,Frescues, but it is the person in the
OL,13,Fwater that can spot the first warning
OL,14,Fsigns.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1780575067
OL,3,CEmergency teams highlight open water
OL,4,Cdangers
OL,6,FAnother St Abbs Independent Lifeboat
OL,7,Fcrew member, Bob Meins, explains more
OL,8,Fabout cold water shock, and why you
OL,9,Fshould think twice before jumping in a
OL,10,Friver, "You never know what's in the
OL,11,Fwater. These are the dangers. When the
OL,12,Ftemperatures are so hot, the water is
OL,13,Fhot in the first six inches. And then
OL,14,Fas you go down, it gets colder and
OL,15,Fcolder, so you get cold water shock."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1780575067
OL,3,CEmergency teams highlight open water
OL,4,Cdangers
OL,6,FThe local swimming group is also keen
OL,7,Fto spread the message of how to stay
OL,8,Fsafe. Sharron MacPherson swims with
OL,9,Fthe Coldingham Brave Bayer group and
OL,10,Fshares her experience, "You have to
OL,11,Flisten to your body and get out,
OL,12,Factually, almost at the point where
OL,13,Fyou think, this is fantastic, I could
OL,14,Fstay here forever. That is your sign
OL,15,Fto get out because your body's
OL,16,Factually telling you fibs. It's
OL,17,Fconning you to think that you're
OL,18,Factually in a better place than you
OL,19,Fare. It's one of the very first stages
OL,20,Fof being very cold."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1780575067
OL,3,CEmergency teams highlight open water
OL,4,Cdangers
OL,6,FEvery life lost to drowning is a
OL,7,Fdevastating loss to their friends and
OL,8,Ffamily, but the safety messages are
OL,9,Fnot about staying dry, but rather to
OL,10,Fbe responsible, know the warning
OL,11,Fsigns, and what to do if something
OL,12,Fgoes wrong. Their advice includes:
OL,14,FFloat to Live
OL,16,FOne of the key messages of the day was
OL,17,F'float to live', the advice to float
OL,18,Fon your back if you get caught by the
OL,19,Fcurrent or are experiencing shortness
OL,20,Fof breathe from cold water shock.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1780575067
OL,3,CEmergency teams highlight open water
OL,4,Cdangers
OL,6,FRNLI Lieguard Bradley Schreiber
OL,7,Fexplains, "So you float on your back,
OL,8,Fpoint your belly up to the sky as high
OL,9,Fas you can. Put your ears below the
OL,10,Fwater. Keep your nose and your mouth
OL,11,Fpointed to the sky, and spread
OL,12,Fyourself out like a starfish - so legs
OL,13,Fand arms spread out - and you move
OL,14,Fyour hands back and forth really
OL,15,Fslowly. You want to do that for about
OL,16,F60 to 90 seconds, until you've
OL,17,Facclimatised to the water and your
OL,18,Fheart rate and breathing rate have
OL,19,Fstarted to slow down."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1780575067
OL,3,CEmergency teams highlight open water
OL,4,Cdangers
OL,6,FSwimmers visiting the beach as the
OL,7,Fwater safety event unfolded agreed it
OL,8,Fis important to remember these
OL,9,Fmessages. One told ITV Border, "It's
OL,10,Fsuper important, especially now in the
OL,11,Fsummer. People really don't know much
OL,12,Fabout the waters and sea and tides."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/9
